      <title>拜登赦免数千项联邦大麻指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/biden-pardons-many-federal-marijuana-charges-commutes-others</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·拜登总统赦免了数千名因在某些联邦土地上使用或持有大麻而被定罪的美国人，并对近十几名非暴力毒品犯罪者减刑，这与他去年采取的强调司法改革议程的举措相呼应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/biden-pardons-many-federal-marijuana-charges-commutes-others</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 13:34:37 GMT</pubDate>
